    },
    {
        "author": ".vbuterin",
        "category": "Execution R\u0026D",
        "parent": "",
        "content": "So instead of `max_child_gas = parent_gas - len(parent_memory) * k`, it's `sqrt(max_child_gas) = sqrt(parent_gas) - len(parent_memory) * k`",
